                        ana="http://syriaca.org/keyword/death http://syriaca.org/keyword/miracles">
                        <desc><persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/3602">Two children</persName>
                            were were struck down with illness and died when their <persName
                                ref="http://syriaca.org/person/3601">parents</persName> refused
