                <idno type="URI">http://syriaca.org/spear/808-30</idno>
                <listEvent>
                    <event ana="http://syriaca.org/keyword/religious-practices">
                        <desc> For twenty-six years <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/2097">
                                Simeon </persName> preached, gave blessings, and established himself
                            as a spiritual teacher as the church he established flourished. </desc>
